RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DISTINCT(COUNTERPARTY),b.customer_name1 FROM OLTB_CONTRACT_MASTER A,OLTM_CUSTOMER b WHERE CUSIP_NO IN(SELECT DISTINCT(CUSIP_NO) FROM TLTBS_FMEM_LOR_INT_PARAMS WHERE CUSIP_NO IS NOT NULL) AND A.COUNTERPARTY = B.CUSTOMER_NO
SELECT DISTINCT(CUSIP_NO) FROM TLTB_FMEM_LOR_INT_PARAMS WHERE CUSIP_NO IS NOT NULL
SELECT DISTINCT(LOR_SEQUENCE) FROM TLTB_FMEM_LOR_INT_PARAMS WHERE BORROWER=? AND END_DATE = ? AND LOR_SEQUENCE IS NOT NULL ORDER BY LOR_SEQUENCE

Select ii.counterparty, ii.branch, ii.Module, ii.product_code, ii.currency, ii.ssi_mnemonic, ii.settlement_seq_no, ii.pay_account, ii.recv_account From oltm_instr ii Where ii.counterparty IN (?, 'ALL') AND ii.currency IN (?, '*.*') AND ii.module IN ('LB', 'TL', 'AL') AND ii.product_code = 'ALL' AND ii.branch IN (?, 'ALL')
